1588:../.././hal//stm32f3/CMSIS/core/core_cm4.h ****   \brief   Set Priority Grouping
1589:../.././hal//stm32f3/CMSIS/core/core_cm4.h ****   \details Sets the priority grouping field using the required unlock sequence.
